      • onDoubleTap

        boolean onDoubleTap(float x,
                  float y)
        Called immediately after the second time a touch is lifted in a double tap gesture The allowable duration between taps is determined by ViewConfiguration
        Parameters:
        x - The x screen coordinate of the tapped point
        y - The y screen coordinate of the tapped point
        Returns:
        True if the event is consumed, false if the event should continue to propagate
